<doc id="237819" wikidata="Q7413287" url="?curid=237819" title="San Antonio, Cayo">
<text>San Antonio is a village in the Cayo District of Belize. In 2000, the village of San Antonio had a population of 2,124 people. Its population is predominantly Yukatek-speaking Maya.

